name: i carry your heart with me - original valentine collage aceo
description: i carry your heart with me - original aceo 2.5 x 3.5 standard ACEO size each collage is made on hand cut cold pressed heavy weight (#140lb) acid free strathmore watercolor paper - & packaged in a glassine bag tied in baker's twine collage made with archival ink & paper, hand-stamped comes signed, titled, dated & numbered each card will come in a clear polypropylene, pvc & acid free & archival safe ultra*pro sleeve measuring 2 5/8" X 3 5/8" words from a poem by e.e. cummings what is an art card, ATC, ACEO? ATC stands for Artist Trading Card, ACEO stands for Art Cards, Editions & Originals. these cards have one main rule - they are 3.5 inches by 2.5 inches - the size of a trading card. the reason for this is, of course, that art cards are made to be traded! but while artists were happily trading cards, the general public was left out in the cold, having no art cards to trade. a group of artists realized this, & quickly made their cards available for sale at remarkably low prices so that everyone could join in the fun! cards are sold either as originals or editions & are collectible. peace to you, thanks for looking!
